data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","sequence_number":220,"item_id":"msg_01b64be3e2ebadec00693a2d5750608196b146652be8452263","output_index":2,"content_index":0,"text":"Contoso Electronics has established a Whistleblower Policy to maintain a safe and transparent working environment. This policy encourages employees to report any unethical or illegal activities. Here are key elements of the policy:\n\n1. **Reporting Procedures**: \n   - Contact the Human Resources Department.\n   - Email the Compliance Officer at compliance@contoso.com.\n   - Call the Compliance Hotline at 1-800-555-1212.\n\n2. **Details Required for Reporting**:\n   - Time and date of the incident.\n   - Individuals involved.\n   - Description of the event.\n   - Any evidence related to the incident.\n\n3. **Anonymity**: Reports can be made anonymously by calling the Compliance Hotline.\n\n4. **Retaliation**: Retaliation against whistleblowers is strictly prohibited and will lead to disciplinary action, including termination.\n\n5. **Confidentiality**: The identity of whistleblowers will be kept confidential as permitted by law.\n\n6. **Investigation**: All reported incidents will be promptly and thoroughly investigated.","logprobs":[]}

